The "Clear" button is used to reset the total to zero. 
The "Done" button can be used to lower the current key pad.
The "Total" button is used to add the current price and quantity to the total and display that value and it's formula.
Price must be a number with at most one decimal place. Quantity must be an integer with no decimal place. 
"Total" will simply clear quantity or price if the input doesn't make sense. 
